The default value for C<automaticResponseStatus> is C<IGNORED>. The
value for C<automaticResponseAction> is only required when
C<automaticResponseStatus> is set to C<ENABLED>. The default value for
C<overrideCustomerWebaclClassic> is C<false>.

For other resource types that you can protect with a Shield Advanced
policy, this C<ManagedServiceData> configuration is an empty string.

